<TITLE> China`s Wen targets fast growth, curbing inflation </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Beijing, March 18 (bdnews24.com/Reuters) - Chinese Premier Wen Jiabao is holding his annual news conference following the closing session of the National People's Congress, or parliament. Following are highlights: GROWTH AND INFLATION "We need to ensure fast, yet steady economic development in this country and at the same time we need to effectively hold down inflation. We must pay attention to the problems of instability, lack of coordination and unsustainability in the economy "There must be new breakthroughs in political and economic reforms. We need to stick to liberating our thinking."
